<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="3" n="14">죵즁 츄고를 베플미</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="3" n="15">엇더ᄒᆞ올ᄂᆞᆫ지 ᄒᆞ얏더니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="3" n="16">十월 十五일</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="3" n="17">봉디 ᄂᆡ에 의쥬ᄒᆞ고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="3" n="18">죵즁 츄고ᄒᆞ라 ᄒᆞᄋᆞᆸ시다</sent>
